text: Abdul Malek is a Bangladesh Awami League politician and the former Member of Parliament of Mymensingh-4. He was the organizer of the Liberation War of Bangladesh. == Career == Abdul Malek was elected to parliament from Mymensingh-4 as a Bangladesh Awami League candidate in 1973. He was the organizer of the Liberation War of Bangladesh. == References == Category:1934 births Category:Bangladeshi politicians Category:People from Mymensingh Division Category:2016 deaths Category:1st Jatiya Sangsad members
